								</svg>
							</button>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</nav>

		<!-- Hero Section -->
		<section class="hero">
			<div class="hero-content">
				<h1 class="hero-title">Handmade with love</h1>
				<p class="hero-subtitle">Each piece tells a story, crafted with passion and decades of artistry</p>
